comments: Lopez (MIL) clamps Adebayo's (MIA) arm and affects his ability to retrieve the loose ball.
Crowder (MIA) initiates contact by placing his hand to Antetokounmpo's (MIL) front during his drive and affects his SQBR. The contact from Crowder occurs prior to any contact from Antetokounmpo.
Adebayo (MIA) is established in Middleton's (MIL) path and absorbs the contact during the dribble hand-off.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) gathers on his left foot and takes two legal steps.
Adebayo (MIA) makes contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) arm during his driving shot attempt.
Matthews' (MIL) momentum is carrying him backward when Butler (MIA) releases the contact without pushing-off as he steps back toward the perimeter.
Dragic (MIA) retracts his arm from Bledsoe's (MIL) body during his drive and doesn't affect his SQBR.
Bledsoe (MIL) gathers the ball and takes two legal steps prior to passing.
Adebayo (MIA) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) that affects his shot attempt.
Crowder (MIA) and Middleton (MIL) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Crowder (MIA) after he releases his jump shot attempt.

Dragic (MIA) cleanly dislodges the ball from Middleton (MIL) prior to the incidental contact on the perimeter. After communicating with the Replay Center, the possession is correctly awarded to the Bucks.
A delay-of-game warning is issued to the Bucks.
Herro (MIA) and Lopez (MIL) engage and separate prior to the inbound pass.
Korver (MIL) makes contact with Butler's (MIA) arm that affects his balance after he gathers the pass.
Hill (MIL) is standing on the sideline when he makes contact with the ball.
Butler (MIA) jumps out of bounds and touches the floor before releasing the ball back inbounds.
Dragic (MIA) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact from Lopez (MIL) during the shot attempt near the rim.
Butler (MIA) establishes himself in a screening position in Hill's (MIL) path and gives him a step to avoid the contact.
Matthews (MIL) and Butler (MIA) engage and separate as Butler receives the inbound pass.
DiVincenzo (MIL) makes contact with Butler's (MIA) arm prior to the ball contact as Butler receives the pass.
Dragic (MIA) steps forward after Middleton (MIL) has started his upward shooting motion toward the rim, and Middleton lands on Dragic during a natural shooting motion as he returns to the floor.
Herro (MIA) is established in Matthews' (MIL) path and absorbs the upper body contact during the screen.

Butler (MIA) is in the air in a natural shooting motion when Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with his midsection and affects his trajectory and balance. The shot is taken before the expiration of time, and the foul occurred before Butler landed.
